#import "/_lib/0.1.1.typ": *
#show: template

#taxon[Definition]
#title[Tangent space to a point of a manifold]

For a #local("009D")[smooth manifold] $M$ with atlas $A$ we define the _tangent space_ to the point $x$ in $M$ to be the following set of equivalence classes

$
  { (phi, v) | phi in A, v in RR^n}\/~,
$
where $(phi,v) ~ (psi,w) :<==> D_(phi(x))  (psi @ phi^(-1))(w) = v$.
